%20Pradhan%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20member%20has%20raised%20a%20question%20which%20is%20not%20related%20to%20the%20question%20put%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20I%20like%20to%20assure%20the%20House%20through%20you%2C%20this%20government%20is%20committed%20to%20total%20socio-psychological%20and%20mental%20protection%20of%20all%20students%2C%20whether%20they%20are%20studying%20in%20a%20coaching%20center%2C%20in%20an%20institution%2C%20school%20education%20or%20higher%20education%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20exhaustive%20and%20detailed%20guidelines%20on%20coaching%20centers%20were%20issued%20to%20all%20states%20in%20January%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20states%20also%20have%20regulations%2C%20like%20Rajasthan%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Goa.%20They%20have%20their%20own%20regulations%20to%20look%20into%20the%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRegarding%20the%20protection%2C%20this%20is%20a%20socio-psychological%20issue.%20We%20all%20have%20to%20take%20care.%20This%20is%20not%20an%20issue%20to%20be%20dealt%20with%20through%20only%20allegations%20and%20answers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20civil%20services%20aspirants%20died%20on%20Saturday%20after%20the%20basement%20of%20a%20building%20housing%20a%20coaching%20centre%20in%20central%20Delhi's%20Old%20Rajinder%20Nagar%20area%20was%20flooded%20following%20heavy%20rains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20reply%20to%20another%20question%2C%20Mr%20Pradhan%20dismissed%20that%20India%20was%20witnessing%20%26quot%3Bbrain-drain%26quot%3B%20with%20students%20going%20abroad%20for%20higher%20education.%20The%20students%20who%20go%20outside%20have%20made%20the%20country%20proud%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETMC%20MP%20Saugata%20Roy%20asked%20if%20the%20number%20of%20students%20going%20abroad%20is%20increasing.%20He%20said%20good%20quality%20higher%20education%20not%20being%20available%20in%20India%20