otect%20our%20fundamental%20rights%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESir%2C%20I%20am%20Avinash%20Dubey%20who%20is%20staying%20in%20Delhi's%20Mukherjee%20Nagar%20and%20preparing%20for%20civil%20services.%20Yesterday%2C%20on%2027%20July%202024%2C%203%20of%20our%20student%20mates%20who%20were%20preparing%20for%20Civil%20Services%20in%20a%20coaching%20institute%20in%20Old%20Rajendra%20Nagar%20lost%20their%20lives%20in%20an%20unfortunate%20manner%20without%20any%20fault%20of%20theirs.%20It%20has%20come%20to%20light%20that%20some%20students%20were%20taking%20coaching%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20a%20coaching%20institute.%20Due%20to%20rain%2C%20the%20basement%20was%20flooded%20and%20the%203%20students%20lost%20their%20lives%20after%20getting%20trapped%20there.%20Sir%2C%20areas%20like%20Mukherjee%20Nagar%2C%20Old%20Rajendra%20Nagar%20of%20Delhi%20have%20been%20facing%20the%20problem%20of%20waterlogging%20every%20year%20due%20to%20the%20apathy%20of%20the%20municipality%20here.%20Due%20to%20lack%20of%20cleanliness%2C%20the%20drain%20water%20reaches%20the%20main%20road%20and%20sometimes%20even%20enters%20houses.%20We%20have%20to%20walk%20through%20knee-deep%20drain%20water.%20Sir%2C%20due%20to%20the%20indifference%20of%20the%20municipality%20and%20the%20Delhi%20government%2C%20today%20students%20like%20us%20are%20living%20a%20hell-like%20life%20for%20our%20preparation.%20Students%20like%20us%20are%20moving%20towards%20our%20goals%20by%20whatever%20means%20we%20can.%20But%2C%20yesterday's%20incident%20has%20proved%20that%20the%20lives%20of%20students%20are%20not%20safe.%20Delhi%20government%20and%20municipality%20have%20made%20us%20helpless%20just%20like%20insects.%20Sir%2C%20it%20is%20our%20fundamental%20right%20to%20study%20while%20living%20a%20healthy%20life%2C%20unfortunately%20the%20Delhi%20government%20and%20municipality%20are%20completely%20indifferent%20to%20it%20due%20to%20which%20the%20lives%20of%20students%20like%20us%20are%20in%20danger.%20The%20above%20inciden