0Moun%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20remained%20in%20touch%20with%20him%20till%20March%2012%20and%20he%20was%20quite%20upset%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Indian%20embassy's%20reply%20to%20Ajay%20Moun's%20letter%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20embassy%20had%20requested%20the%20concerned%20Russian%20authorities%20for%20confirmation%20of%20his%20death%20and%20transportation%20of%20his%20mortal%20remains%20requested%20by%20you.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20Russian%20side%20has%20confirmed%20his%20death.%20However%2C%20to%20identify%20the%20body%2C%20they%20need%20a%20DNA%20test%20from%20his%20close%20relatives%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjay%20Moun%20also%20requested%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20bring%20his%20brother's%20mortal%20remains%20back%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20have%20enough%20money%20to%20bring%20back%20his%20body%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20sold%20off%20a%20one-acre%20land%20and%20spent%20Rs%2011.50%20lakh%20to%20send%20him%20to%20Russia%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Russia%20agreed%20to%20India's%20demand%20to%20ensure%20early%20release%20and%20return%20of%20Indian%20nationals%20working%20in%20the%20Russian%20military%20as%20support%20staff%20after%20Modi%20raised%20the%20issue%20with%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20had%20promised%20early%20discharge%20of%20all%20Indian%20nationals%20from%20the%20army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20said%20the%20issue%20of%20Indian%20nationals%20serving%20in%20the%20Russian%20Army%20remained%20a%20matter%20of%20%26quot%3Butmost%20concern%26quot%3B%20and%20demanded%20action%20from%20Moscow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflict%20in%20eastern%20Europe%20has%20been%20raging%20since%20February%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20ha