0in%20the%20basement.%20The%20coaching%20centre%20gave%20incorrect%20information.%20We%20have%20also%20informed%20the%20MCD%20(Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi)%20so%20that%20they%20can%20cancel%20the%20building's%20NOC.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20yesterday%20reported%20that%20the%20MCD%20No-Objection%20Certificate%2C%20too%2C%20said%20that%20the%20basement%20is%20to%20be%20used%20for%20parking%20or%20storage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20certificate%20issued%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20fire%20department%20had%20said%20the%20building%20has%20complied%20with%20fire%20safety%20requirements.%20It%20added%20that%20the%20basement%20should%20be%20used%20strictly%20as%20per%20building%20bye-laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20building%20bye-laws%20lay%20down%20that%20adequate%20arrangement%20shall%20be%20made%20to%20ensure%20surface%20drainage%20does%20not%20enter%20the%20basement.%20They%20also%20say%20that%20if%20the%20basement%20is%20used%20for%20office%20and%20commercial%20purposes%2C%20there%20should%20be%20a%20sufficient%20number%20of%20exit%20ways%20and%20access%20ways.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20this%20coaching%2C%20there%20was%20only%20one%20entry%2Fexit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECivil%20service%20aspirants%20Tania%20Soni%20and%20Shreya%20Yadav%2C%20both%2025%2C%20and%20Navin%20Delvin%2C%2028%20died%20after%20heavy%20rain%20in%20Delhi%20Saturday%20led%20to%20flooding%20of%20the%20basement.%20Twenty-odd%20students%20were%20in%20the%20library%20in%20the%20basement%20when%20water%20gushed%20in.%20While%20most%20were%20rescued%2C%20three%20drowned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20has%20sparked%20massive%20protests%20and%20political%20backlash%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20protesters%20targeting%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20which%20is%20in%20power%20in%20Delhi%20and%20also%20controls%20the%20MCD.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20mayor%20Shelly%20Oberoi%20has%20ordered%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20incident%20to%20find%20out%20if%20any%20MCD%20officer%20is%20involved%20in%20the%20negligence%20that%20led%20to%20the%20tragedy.%20She%20has%20also%20said%20all%20coaching%20centres%20that%20have%20violated%20the%20law%20would%20face%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%20seven%20people%2C%20including%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20coaching%20centre%20and%20the%20building%2C%20have%20been%20arrested.%20They%20face%20charges%20of%20culpable%20homicide%20not%20amounting%20to%20murder%20and%20causing%20death%20by%20negligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722243840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fbp69444g_delhi-basement-tragedy_625x300_29_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fraus-ias-rajendra-nagar-delhi-basement-tragedy-delhi-coaching-centre-loses-fire-safety-nod-after-basement-tragedy-kills-3-6213855%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20days%20after%20three%20IAS%20aspirants%20died%20due%20to%20waterlogging%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20a%20coaching%20centre%20in%20Delhi's%20Rajinder%20Nagar%2C%20the%20fire%20department%20has%20started%20the%20process%20of%20cancelling%20the%20fire%20safety%20clearance%20of%20the%20building%20the%20coaching%20centre%20is%20in%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fraus-ias-rajendra-nagar-delhi-basement-tragedy-delhi-coaching-centre-loses-fire-safety-nod-after-basement-tragedy-kills-3-6213855%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fraus-ias-rajendra-nagar-delhi-basement-tragedy-delhi-coaching-centre-loses-fire-safety-nod-after-basement-tragedy-kills-3-6213855%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fraus-ias-rajendra-nagar-delhi-basement-tragedy-delhi-coaching-centre-loses-fire-safety-nod-after-basement-tragedy-kills-3-6213855%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22We%20put%20Elon%20Musk's%20dream%20to%20colonize%20Mars%20up%20against%20Jef