iling%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENIP%20Group%20makes%20money%20from%20live%20streams%20%E2%80%94%20both%20of%20esports%20and%20from%20third-party%20influencers%20%E2%80%94%20and%20event%20production%20and%20its%20esports%20arm.%20The%20company's%20relatively%20small-scale%20IPO%20raised%20%2420%20million%2C%20and%20Ho's%20stake%20was%20worth%20%2469%20million%20as%20of%20Friday's%20market%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENIP%20Group%20plans%20to%20explore%20esports%20real%20estate%2C%20digital%20collectibles%2C%20and%20esports%20training%20camps%2C%20among%20other%20strategies%2C%20the%20company%20said%20in%20a%20filing.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHo%20and%2035-year-old%20Hicham%20Chahine%20are%20the%20co-CEOs%20of%20NIP%20Group%2C%20a%20holding%20company%20with%20subsidiaries%20in%20Sweden%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChahine%2C%20a%20former%20hedge%20fund%20manager%20for%20Oslo-based%20wealth%20management%20firm%20Formue%2C%20runs%20the%20company's%20Western%20operations%20in%20Sweden.%20Ho%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20runs%20the%20business%20in%20Asia%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company's%20SEC%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20duo%20cofounded%20NIP%20Group%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msigroup.com.hk%2Fteam%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHo%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20the%20chief%20marketing%20officer%20of%20iDreamsky%20Games%2C%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20game%20publishers%20in%20China.%20He%20said%20on%20a%20company%20website%20that%20he%20was%20the%20youngest-ever%20graduate%20of%20the%20MIT%20Sloan%20School%20of%20Management's%20master%20of%20finance%20program.%20Ho%20is%20also%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Macau%20Esports%20Federation%20and%20the%20vice-chairman%20of%20MSI%20Finance%20Management%20Company%2C%20a%20Hong%20Kong-based%20family%20office%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHo%20is%20the%20youngest%20son%20of%20Macau%20casino%20heavyweight%20Stanley%20Ho.%20The%20patriarch%2C%20who%20had%2017%20children%20with%20four%20wives%2C%20died%20in%202020.%20Bloomberg%20estimates%20his%20family's%20net%20worth%20at%20%2413%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20chose%20to%20do%20something%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20Mario%20Ho%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-07-26%2Fcasino-tycoon-s-son-builds-his-own-fortune-with-e-sports-ipo%3Fsrnd%3Dhomepage-asia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Bloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIn%20my%20lifetime%2C%20I%20want%20to%20write%20my%20own%20stories.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ee181857-fe51-4e32-8154-6aa68c055fba%5C%22%3ELoan%20and%20payments%20to%20Ho%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20company's%20SEC%20filing%2C%20in%202023%2C%20NIP%20Group's%20annual%20revenue%20grew%2027%25%20to%20%2483.7%20million.%20The%20company%20lost%20%2413.3%20million%20last%20year%2C%20compared%20with%20a%20%246.3%20million%20loss%20in%202022.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20did%20not%20publish%20more%20recent%20financial%20data%2C%20but%20it%20said%20in%20the%20filing%20that%20it%20may%20not%20hit%20profitability%20%E2%80%94%20standard%20language%20for%20most%20unprofitable%20companies%20going%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20filing%20also%20showed%20that%20in%202022%2C%20NIP%20Group%20issued%20a%20loan%20to%20Ho%20of%20nearly%20%24300%2C000.%20The%20following%20year%2C%20NIP%20Group%20paid%20Ho%20over%20%24814%2C000%20for%20%26quot%3Breality%20show%20services.%26quot%3B%20The%20company%20made%20less%20than%20%24200%2C000%20in%20revenue%20last%20year%20from%20its%20reality%20show%20service%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20its%20esports%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20billed%20as%20an%20esports%20company%2C%20NIP%20Group%20made%20the%20bulk%20of%20its%20revenue%20last%20year%20primarily%20from%20managing%2036%2C000%20online%20entertainers%20%E2%80%94%20with%20money%20comin