ching-on-par-with-us-military-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Wednesday%20Last%20Day%20To%20File%20Income%20Tax%20Returns%3A%20What%20Happens%20If%20You%20Miss%20It%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20deadline%20for%20filing%20Income%20Tax%20Returns%20(ITR)%20is%20fast%20approaching%2C%20with%20taxpayers%20urged%20to%20submit%20their%20returns%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20month%20to%20avoid%20penalties%20and%20fines.%20The%20Income%20Tax%20Department%20has%20set%20a%20July%2031%20deadline%20to%20file%20ITR%20for%20FY%202023-24.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20speculation%20and%20demands%20for%20an%20extension%2C%20the%20deadline%20for%20filing%20ITR%C2%A0is%20unlikely%20to%20be%20pushed%20further.%20Last%20year%2C%20too%2C%20a%20large%20number%20of%20taxpayers%20were%20caught%20off%20guard%20when%20the%20deadline%20was%20not%20extended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaxpayers%20are%20advised%20to%20prepare%20and%20file%20their%20returns%20on%20time%20to%20avoid%20penalties%20and%20fines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20happens%20if%20you%20miss%20the%20ITR%20deadline%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20CA%20Chirag%20Chauhan%2C%20failing%20to%20file%20ITR%20before%20the%20deadline%20might%20have%20%26quot%3Bserious%20consequences%26quot%3B%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20you%20need%20to%20know%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20old%20tax%20regime%20option%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20opted%20for%20the%20old%20tax%20regime%2C%20missing%20the%20deadline%20could%20lead%20to%20losing%20its%20benefits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%20you%20miss%20the%20deadline%2C%20you%20will%20be%20automatically%20shifted%20to%20the%20new%20tax%20regime%20--%20the%20default%20option.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20old%20tax%20regime%20offers%20several%20deductions%20and%20exemptions%2C%20such%20as%20those%20for%20investments%20and%20specific%20incomes.%20The%20new%20regime%20does%20not%20provide%20these%20benefits%2C%20leading%20to%20potentially%20higher%20taxes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESwitching%20to%20the%20new%20regime%20might%20increase%20your%20tax%20liability%2C%20and%20you%20may%20also%20have%20to%20pay%20interest%20on%20the%20outstanding%20tax%20amount.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20significant%20impact%20will%20be%20on%20those%20who%20prefer%20the%20old%20tax%20regime.%20Missing%20the%20ITR%20deadline%20means%20losing%20the%20option%20to%20choose%20the%20old%20regime%2C%20which%20many%20are%20unaware%20of.%20This%20new%20provision%20applies%20to%20FY%2023-24%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELate%20fee%2Fpenalty%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20you%20miss%20the%20deadline%2C%20you%20can%20still%20file%20a%20late%20return%2C%20but%20this%20comes%20with%20penalties%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELate%20filing%20fee%3A%20Under%20Section%20234F%20of%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Act%2C%20a%20late%20filing%20fee%20of%20Rs%205%2C000%20can%20be%20imposed.%20If%20your%20income%20is%20below%20Rs%205%20lakh%2C%20the%20fee%20is%20reduced%20to%20Rs%201%2C000.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EInterest%20on%20outstanding%20tax%3A%20According%20to%20Section%20234A%2C%20you%20will%20be%20charged%20interest%20at%20a%20rate%20of%201%20per%20cent%20per%20month%2C%20or%20part%20thereof%2C%20on%20the%20outstanding%20tax%20amount%20from%20the%20due%20date.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20carry%20forward%20of%20loss%20and%20setoff%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFiling%20your%20ITR%20on%20time%20is%20necessary%20if%20you%20have%20incurred%20losses%20from%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20mutual%20funds%2C%20properties%2C%20or%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECarry%20forward%20losses%3A%20Filing%20your%20ITR%20on%20time%20allows%20you%20to%20carry%20forward%20losses%20to%20offset%20them%20against%20future%20income%2C%20which%20reduces%20future%20tax%20liabilities.%3C%2