20quoted%20CMIE%20data%20about%20the%20employment%20rate%20-%20which%20is%20the%20'proportion%20of%20employed%20persons%20in%20the%20working%20age%20population'%20-%20recorded%20at%2037%25%20in%20June%202024.%20The%20Global%20Hunger%20Index%202023%20was%20often%20referred%20to%20last%20week%20in%20Parliament%20-%20India%20ranked%20111th%20out%20of%20125%20countries.%20Despite%20improvements%20in%20food%20production%20and%20distribution%2C%20food%20insecurity%20persists%2C%20particularly%20in%20marginalised%20communities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EImpact%20On%20Personal%20Freedoms%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20citizen%20cannot%20truly%20enjoy%20any%20liberty%20when%20perpetually%20anxious%20about%20her%20family's%20unmet%20needs.%20This%20becomes%20even%20more%20important%20when%20the%20Budget%20skirts%20around%20the%20issues%20of%20health%2C%20nutrition%2C%20social%20security%2C%20and%20education.%20It%20is%20difficult%20to%20think%20about%20personal%20liberties%20on%20an%20empty%20stomach.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMGNREGA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMGNREGA%20addresses%20the%20issue%20of%20Right%20to%20Work.%20However%2C%20it%20ensures%20it%20as%20a%20statutory%20right%2C%20instead%20of%20being%20a%20Fundamental%20Right.%20The%20latter%20cannot%20be%20taken%20away%20by%20an%20amendment%20of%20the%20MGNREGA%20Act.%20It%20bears%20repetition%20that%20states%20have%20been%20constantly%20deprived%20of%20MGNREGA%20funds.%20The%20Union%20owes%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government%20alone%20Rs%207%2C000%20Crores%20for%20the%20scheme.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20labour-surplus%20society%2C%20why%20then%20is%20the%20Union%20government%20often%20selling%20the%20family%20silver%20to%20private%20entities%3F%20Two%20dozen%20large%20Public%20Sector%20Undertakings%20(PSUs)%20have%20been%20privatised.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20solution.%20Should%20it%20not%20be%20the%20duty%20of%20the%20state%20to%20offer%20the%20labour%20force%20multiple%20opportunities%20for%20employment%3F%20There%20are%2030%20lakh%20vacancies%20in%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20government-controlled%20organisations.%20What%20is%20the%20road%20map%20and%20timelines%20for%20these%20vacancies%20to%20be%20filled%3F%20Parliament%20is%20in%20session.%20The%20government%20must%20provide%20answers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEducation%20And%20Skill%20Development%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20has%20an%20obligation%20to%20provide%20quality%20education%20and%20skill%20development%20to%20improve%20employability%2C%20and%20guarantee%20livelihood.%20But%20Budget%202024%20has%20allocated%20only%20Rs%201.20%20lakh%20crore%20to%20education%2C%20which%20is%20a%202%25%20decline%20from%20Actuals%20(Rs%201.23%20lakh%20crores)%20in%202023-24.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERight%20To%20Livelihood%20As%20A%20Fundamental%20Right%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20judicial%20interpretation%2C%20the%20Right%20to%20Livelihood%20has%20been%20read%20into%20the%20Right%20to%20Life%2C%20even%20though%20it%20is%20not%20explicitly%20listed%20among%20the%20Fundamental%20Rights%20in%20Part%20III%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20emphasised%2C%20%26quot%3BAn%20equally%20important%20facet%20of%20the%20right%20to%20life%20is%20the%20right%20to%20livelihood%20because%20no%20person%20can%20live%20without%20the%20means%20of%20living%2C%20that%20is%2C%20the%20means%20of%20livelihood.%20If%20the%20right%20to%20livelihood%20is%20not%20treated%20as%20a%20part%20of%20the%20constitutional%20right%20to%20life%2C%20the%20easiest%20way%20of%20depriving%20a%20person%20of%20his%20right%20to%20life%20would%20be%20to%20deprive%20him%20of%20his%20means%20of%20livelihood%20to%20the%20point%20of%20abrogation.%20Such%20deprivation%20would%20not%20only%20strip%20life%20of%20its%20effective%20content%20and%20meaningfulness%20but%20also%20make%20life%20impossible%20to%20live.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Right%20to%20Work%2C%20outlined%20in%20the%20directive%20principles%2C%20has%20been%20interpreted%20alongside%20the%20Rights%20to%20Livelihood%20and%20Life%2C%20evolving%20into%20a%20Fundamental%20Right%20through%20judicial%20pronouncements.%20Integrating%20the%20Right%20to%20Work%20into%20Fundamental%20Rights%2C%20and%20ensuring%20that%20policies%20are%20designed%20to%20create%20sustainable%20job%20opportunities%2C%20is%20paramount%20to%20ensuring%20employment.%20Even%20after%20a%20tepid%20performance%20in%20the%20elections%2C%20where%20they%20were%20punished%20by%20young%20people%2C%20this%20government%20refuses%20to%20prioritise%20investment%20in%20education%20and%20vocational%20training.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20talk%20about%20cooperative%20federalism%20will%20not%20do.%20States%20politically%20opposed%20to%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20are%20deprived%20on%20flimsy%20grounds%20for%20years%20of%20their%20MGNREGA%20funds.%20These%20are%20funds%20due%20to%20people%20who%20have%20completed%20their%20work%2C%20and%20have%20still%20not%20been%20paid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20fostering%20a%20more%20inclusive%20job%20market%20by%20supporting%20small%20businesses%20and%20encouraging%20entrepreneurship%20can%20play%20a%20critical%20role%20in%20generating%20employment.%20By%20taking%20these%20steps%2C%20India%20can%20better%20align%20its%20economic%20policies%20with%20its%20constitutional%20commitments%20and%20provide%20more%20meaningful%20support%20to%20its%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Right%20to%20Work%20still%20requires%20the%20state%20to%20take%20responsibility%2C%20and%20appropriate%20legislative%20actions%2C%20to%20fully%20provide%20citizens%20with%20the%20Right%20to%20Life%2C%20Livelihood%2C%20and%20Dignity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EResearch%20Credit%3A%20Chahat%20Mangtani%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Derek%20O'Brien%2C%20MP%2C%20leads%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722236220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fdna2j8po_unemployment_625x300_29_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-12-letter-word-giving-the-government-sleepless-nights-6212589%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20recurring%20theme%20in%20many%20of%20the%20powerful%20interventions%20on%20the%20Budget%20was%20a%2012-letter%20word%20giving%20Modi%20and%20his%20coalition%20sleepless%20Delhi%20nights%3A%20unemployment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-12-letter-word-giving-the-government-sleepless-nights-6212589%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-12-letter-word-giving-the-government-sleepless-nights-6212589%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-12-letter-word-giving-the-government-sleepless-nights-6212589%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sports%20Minister%20Reveals%20Whopping%20Amount%20Spent%20On%20Manu%20Bhaker's%20Training%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Manu%20Bhaker's%20historic%20bronze%20medal%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Paris%20Olympics%202024%2C%20Union%20Sports%20Minister%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%20congratulated%20the%20shooter%20on%20her%20win%20and%20revealed%20the%20hard%20work%20and%20expenditure%20that%20went%20behind%20her%20training.%20Bhaker%20finished%20third%20to%20secure%20a%20bronze%20medal%20in%20the%20final%20of%20the%20Women's%20Air%20Pistol%20event%20on%20Sunday.%20She%20became%20the%20first%20Indian%20woman%20to%20win%20a%20medal%20in%20shooting%20at%20the%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20her%20win%2C%20Mandaviya%20told%20ANI%2C%20%26quot%3BBy%20winning%20the%20first%20bronze%20medal%20in%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%2C%20Manu%20Bhaker%20has%20made%20India%20proud.%20In%20her%20interaction%2C%20she%20said%20that%20she%20has%20been%20a%20part%20of%20'Khelo%20India'.%20I%20am%20delighted%20to%20tell%20you%20that%20PM%20Modi%20started%20'Khelo%20India'%20and%20under%20this%20initiative%2C%20sports%20infrastructure%20was%20set%20up%20in%20the%20country%2C%20sports%20competition%20was%20increased%2C%20and%20projects%20were%20floated%20to%20identify%20sports%20talent%20at%20school%20and%20college%20levels.%20Good%20coaches%20were%20hired%20to%20train%20the%20talents%20identified%2C%20they%20were%20provided%20good%20training%20and%20under%20the%20TOPS%20scheme%2C%20arrangements%20were%20made%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20did%20not%20face%20any%20financial%20constraints.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMandaviya%20revealed%20that%20around%20Rs%202%20crores%20were%20spent%20on%20Manu's%20training%20and%20she%20was%20sent%20to%20Germany%20and%20Switzerland%20for%20it.%20He%20also%20expressed%20confidence%20that%20other%20athletes%20will%20also%20do%20well%20in%20the%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAround%20Rs%202%20crore%20was%20spent%20on%20Manu%20Bhaker's%20training.%20She%20was%20sent%20to%20Germany%20and%20Switzerland%20for%20training.%20Financial%20help%20was%20provided%20which%20was%20needed%20for%20her%20to%20hire%20a%20coach%20who%20she%20wanted.%20We%20are%20providing%20this%20ecosystem%20to%20all%20athletes%20so%20that%20they%20give%20best%20performance%20at%20national%20and%20international%20competitions.%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20our%20athletes%20will%20perform%20well%20in%20Paris%20Olympics%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20shooting%20and%20archery%20competitions%20taking%20place%20today%2C%20Manaviya%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BShooting%20and%20Archery%20competitions%20are%20taking%20place%20today.%20We%20should%20encourage%20our%20athletes%20with%20%23CheerForBharat%20on%20social%20media%20and%20encourage%20them.%20We%20expect%20our%20athletes%20to%20perform%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhaker%20will%20once%20again%20be%20in%20action%20during%20the%2010%20m%20air%20pistol%20mixed%20team%20competition%20qualification%20rounds%20along%20with%20Sarabjot%20Singh%20from%2012%3A45%20PM%20onwards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20shooters%20Ramita%20Jindal%20and%20Arjun%20Babuta%2C%20along%20with%20the%20men's%20archery%20team%2C%20will%20aim%20to%20add%20to%20the%20country's%20medal%20count%20at%20the%20ongoing%20Paris%20Olympics%202024%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20Ramita%20made%20it%20to%20the%20final%20of%20the%20women's%2010%20m%20air%20rifle%20event%20after%20a%20fifth-place%20finish%20during%20the%20qualification%20round%2C%20while%20Arjun%20came%20at%20seventh%20in%20the%20men's%20event.%20The%20top%20eight%20players%20from%20both%20the%20qualification%20rounds%20made%20it%20to%20the%20finals%2C%20which%20are%20scheduled%20for%20today%2C%20as%20per%20Olympics.com.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20the%20men's%20archery%20team%20of%20Dhiraj%20Bommadevara%2C%20Tarundeep%20Rai%20and%20Pravin%20Jadhav%20will%20be%20taking%20on%20Turkiye%20or%20Colombia%20in%20the%20quarterfinals%20at%206%3A31%20PM.%20The%20medal%20rounds%20of%20this%20category%20will%20take%20place%20today%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhaker%20brought%20India's%20first%20medal%20in%20the%20ongoing%20mega%20event%20as%20she%20won%20a%20bronze%20medal%20with%20a%20score%20of%20221.7.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20redemption%20arc%20for%20Manu%20after%20her%20pistol%20malfunctioned%20at%20the%20Tokyo%20Olympics.%20She%20made%20history%20by%20becoming%20the%20first%20Indian%20woman%20in%2020%20years%20to%20reach%20a%20shooting%20final%20in%20an%20individual%20event%20of%20the%20Olympics%20since%20Suma%20Shirur%20in%202004.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Korea's%20Ye%20Jin%20clinched%20the%20gold%20medal%20with%20an%20Olympic%20record%20of%20243.2%20points.%20Her%20compatriot%2C%20Kim%20Yeji%2C%20settled%20for%20silver%20wit