ever%2C%20he%20was%20determined%20to%20prove%20them%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20millions%20of%20rural%20school%20dropouts%20in%20the%20country%20like%20Subhajit%2C%20who%20have%20the%20grit%20and%20determination%20to%20achieve%20goals%20but%20are%20unable%20to%20grow%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20skill%20training.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.larsentoubro.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELarsen%20%26amp%3B%20Toubro%20(L%26amp%3BT)%3C%2Fa%3E%20decided%20to%20bridge%20this%20gap%20in%20the%20construction%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstruction%20is%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20second-largest%20employer%20after%20the%20agriculture%20sector.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3EKnight%20Frank%20%26amp%3B%20RICS%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%2071%20million%20workers%20are%20estimated%20to%20be%20employed%20in%20this%20sector%2C%20but%20only%2019%20percent%20are%20skilled%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20construction%20industry%20is%20poised%20for%20significant%20growth%20in%20the%20coming%20years%2C%20underscoring%20the%20critical%20need%20for%20skilled%20labour.%20To%20meet%20this%20demand%2C%20vocational%20training%20in%20construction%20has%20become%20essential%2C%20equipping%20the%20workforce%20with%20specialised%20skills%20vital%20for%20the%20sector%E2%80%99s%20advancement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnticipating%20this%20need%2C%20L%26amp%3BT%20launched%20the%20first%20Construction%20Skills%20Training%20Institute%20(CSTI)%20in%20Chennai%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20in%201995.%20This%20initiative%20aimed%20to%20develop%20a%20cadre%20of%20well-trained%20professionals%20for%20the%20construction%20industry.%20Over%20the%20past%20three%20decades%2C%20CSTI%20has%20expanded%20to%20nine%20operational%20institutes%2C%20training%20over%203.4%20lakh%20workers%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESkilled%20youth%20trained%20at%20these%20CSTIs%20are%20now%20employed%20by%20top%20construction%20companies%20a