0%9CThey%20know%20that%20their%20education%2C%20experience%2C%20and%20what%20they%20bring%20to%20the%20table%20is%20all%20that%20matters%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVilas%20Dahipale%2C%20an%20LPI%20member%20based%20in%20Pune%20who%20was%20born%20with%20dwarfism%2C%20holds%20an%20engineering%20degree%20but%20got%20rejected%20by%20over%2020%20companies.%20After%20a%20relative%20helped%20him%20get%20a%20job%2C%20he%20worked%20without%20a%20salary%20for%20the%20first%20few%20months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meanwhile%2C%20he%20updated%20his%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20with%20skills%20such%20as%20automation%20testing%2C%20and%20after%20a%20span%20of%20over%203%20years%2C%20he%20has%20now%20been%20offered%20a%20job%20at%20Accenture%20with%20a%20pick-up%2Fdrop-off%20service%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20job%20fair.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20companies%20take%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20online%20but%20don%E2%80%99t%20actually%20consider%20you%20as%20a%20candidate%20if%20you%20have%20a%20disability%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20After%20switching%20various%20fields%20upon%20realising%20his%20limitations%20(for%20instance%2C%20field%20work%20was%20taxing%20for%20Vilas%20given%20his%20height)%2C%20he%20decided%20that%20he%20could%20only%20do%20office-based%20or%20remote%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20admits%20that%20he%20was%20initially%20unaware%20that%20companies%20offer%20jobs%20to%20people%20with%20disabilities.%20%E2%80%9CLearning%20that%20there%20was%20a%20separate%20%E2%80%98handicapped%E2%80%99%20category%20on%20job%20portals%20was%20a%20revelation%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20admits%20Vilas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20he%20revealed%20his%20condition%20on%20job%20portals%2C%20he%20started%20receiving%20calls%20from%20employees%20who%20were%20looking%20to%20hire%20handicapped%20candidates.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20saddest%20part%20is%20that%20most%20companies%20who%20are%20open%20to%20hiring%20candidates%20with%20disabilities%20are%20MNCs%20from%20the%20US%20and%20Europe%2C%20and%20not%20Indian%20companies%2C%E2%80%9D%20rues%20Vilas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrakruthi%2C%20a%2021-year-old%20LPI%20member%20born%20with%20dwarfism%2C%20is%20all%20set%20to%20do%20her%20postgraduate%20diploma%20in%20management.%20She%20says%20that%20she%20is%20afraid%20employers%20won%E2%80%99t%20think%20of%20her%20as%20a%20real%20candidate%20due%20to%20her%20height%2C%20but%20the%20silver%20lining%20is%20that%20she%20has%20the%20job%20fair%20to%20look%20forward%20to%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20done%20two%20internships%20during%20her%20undergraduate%20at%20Teresian%20College%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20she%20admits%20to%20her%20classmates%20taking%20pictures%20of%20her%20and%20mocking%20her%20for%20her%20height%2C%20which%20went%20on%20to%20affect%20her%20marks%20and%20her%20morale.%20But%20she%20took%20a%20stand%20for%20herself%20which%20helped%20her%20blossom%20personally.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20message%20to%20her%20bullies%3F%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20treat%20anyone%20else%20the%20way%20you%20treated%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Disha%20shares%20how%20she%20got%20her%20first%20job%20offer%20in%20Mumbai%20in%20a%20small%20ICICI%20home-loan%20third-party%20office%20after%20giving%2017%20interviews.%20When%20she%20finished%20her%20graduation%20in%20early%202000s%2C%20there%20were%20no%20online%20job%20portals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20only%20classified%20columns%20in%20newspapers%2C%20and%20walk-in%20interviews%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecounting%20an%20experience%20of%20going%20to%20Sab%20TV%20for%20an%20interview%2C%20the%20response%20she%20was%20met%20was%20this%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESab%20kuch%20theek%20hai%2C%20par%20aap%20thode%20alag%20ho%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Everything%20is%20fine%2C%20but%20you%20are%20a%20bit%20different).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20told%20that%20the%20employees%20at%20the%20company%20may%20not%20be%20comfortable%20with%20her%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHiring%20candidates%20with%20disabilities%20is%20not%20something%20that%20most%20corporate%20organisations%20in%20India%20are%20too%20keen%20on%20because%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20it%20as%20directly%20generating%20income%20or%20business%20for%20their%20companies%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ratnaprabha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20social%20awareness%20on%20disability%20has%20increased%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20organisations%20have%20understood%20the%20need%20to%20back%20diverse%20candidates%20and%20have%20started%20to%20more%20thoroughly%20follow%20the%20ES%26amp%3BT%20(Employments%20through%20Skills%2C%20Training%20and%20Placement)%20guidelines.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConducting%20a%20job%20fair%20which%20spreads%20awareness%20on%20issues%20like%20disabilities%2C%20socio-economic%20marginalisation%20and%20caste%2C%20something%20that%20most%20organisations%20shy%20away%20from%2C%20was%20a%20challenge%2C%E2%80%9D%20admits%20Ratnaprabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUrging%20people%20not%20to%20judge%20individuals%20based%20on%20their%20disabilities%2C%20Disha%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CBeing%20judgemental%20is%20a%20disability%20itself%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20even%20visible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20Pictures%20courtesy%3A%20Disha%20Pandya%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC10009251%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DCensus%25202011%2520and%2520recently%2520held%2C2011%252C%2520respectively%2520(4)%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC10009251%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DCensus%25202011%2520and%2520recently%2520held%2C2011%252C%2520respectively%2520(4)%3C%2Fa%3E.%20National%20Library%20of%20