so%20been%20recognised%20by%20the%20Kerala%20Government%20for%20his%20efforts%20in%20organic%20farming.%20He%20has%20been%20awarded%20the%20Kera%20Kesari%20Award%20in%202017%2C%20the%20Yuva%20Kesari%20Award%20in%202019%2C%20and%20the%20Akshayasree%20Award%202022-23%20for%20Best%20Organic%20Farming%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20farm%20was%20set%20up%20and%20started%20running%20smoothly%2C%20he%20was%20filled%20with%20the%20desire%20to%20share%20his%20knowledge%20with%20the%20next%20generation.%20%E2%80%9CMerely%20one%20person%20practising%20a%20sustainable%20model%20of%20farming%20is%20of%20no%20good%20if%20that%20information%20is%20not%20shared.%20I%20wanted%20to%20educate%20other%20farmers%20and%20students%20about%20healthy%20ways%20to%20grow%20food%2C%20consume%20food%20and%20practice%20farming%20that%20is%20beneficial%20to%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaravanan%20conducts%20classes%20for%20the%20Kerala%20Government%20under%20the%20Bhartiya%20Prakritik%20Krishi%20Paddhti%20(BPKP)%20and%20the%20Paramparagath%20Krishi%20Vikas%20Yojana%20(PKVY)%20scheme.%20With%20at%20least%20three%20classes%20per%20week%2C%20he%20claims%20to%20have%20educated%20over%2015%2C000%20farmers%20and%20students%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESreedhu%20P%2C%20agricultural%20officer%2C%20Perumatty%2C%20says%20that%20Saravanan%E2%80%99s%20farm%20is%20a%20perfect%20example%20of%20how%20an%20organic%20farm%20should%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201090px)%20100vw%2C%201090px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan33-1721657916.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221090%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Saravanan%20turned%20his%20family%20farm%20around%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan33-1721657916.jpeg%201090w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F